**Summary:** API reference documentation for the SuperTokens captcha Node.js plugin (`@supertokens-plugins/captcha-nodejs`) that provides CAPTCHA validation for authentication endpoints including signIn, signUp, password reset, and passwordless flows with support for reCAPTCHAv2, reCAPTCHAv3, and Turnstile providers.

**Keywords:**
- @supertokens-plugins/captcha-nodejs
- CaptchaPluginError
- SuperTokensPluginCaptchaConfig
- reCAPTCHAv2/reCAPTCHAv3/turnstile
- ShouldValidate interface
- signInPOST/signUpPOST/passwordResetPOST
- generatePasswordResetTokenPOST
- consumeCodePOST/createCodePOST
- validateCaptcha function
- ReCaptchaV2Response/ReCaptchaV3Response/TurnstileResponse
- SuperTokensPlugin init
- PLUGIN_ID supertokens-plugin-captcha
- secretKey configuration
- captcha validation endpoints